Introduction

Sunwoo (real name: Lee Sunwoo) is a South Korean trainee under Evermore Entertainment. She is a member of the pre-debut group EVERMORE MUSE. She is known for her appearances on the competitive reality TV shows Top 10 Student, Girls Planet 999, Stars Awakening, and Universe Ticket. On January 17, 2024, She made it to the final episode of Universe Ticket, but ultimately ended up being eliminated.
